Black lives matter.

25:27.613 --> 25:30.311
- We will not stand...

25:30.354 --> 25:31.573
- That's right!
- Yeah.

25:31.617 --> 25:33.140
- For this
outrageous behavior...

25:33.183 --> 25:34.445
- Right.
- Yes, sir.

25:34.489 --> 25:37.448
- And the utter contempt...

25:37.492 --> 25:40.277
and disregard for black lives.

25:40.321 --> 25:42.236
